<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .feature-box { background-color: white; border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .button { background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Welcome to ScanBite!</h1>
      <p>Your QR-based Takeaway Ordering Platform</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= @user.full_name %></strong>,</p>
      
      <p>Welcome to <strong>ScanBite</strong>! Your email has been successfully verified and your account is now active.</p>
      
      <p><strong>Your Business:</strong> <%= @user.business_name %> (<%= @user.business_type.capitalize %>)</p>
      
      <h3>🚀 Getting Started</h3>
      
      <div class="feature-box">
        <strong>1. Complete Business Setup</strong><br>
        Add your business details, contact information, and UPI ID
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-box">
        <strong>2. Create Your Menu</strong><br>
        Add items with images, prices, and availability
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-box">
        <strong>3. Generate QR Code</strong><br>
        Get your unique QR code for customers to scan
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-box">
        <strong>4. Start Receiving Orders</strong><br>
        Customers scan → Browse Menu → Pay with UPI → You get notified!
      </div>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="https://scanbite.com/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      
      <h3>📱 Key Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Digital Menu Management</li>
        <li>Automatic QR Code Generation</li>
        <li>Order Management System</li>
        <li>Inventory Tracking</li>
        <li>UPI Payment Integration</li>
        <li>Sales Analytics</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>Questions?</strong><br>
      Check our <a href="https://scanbite.com/help" style="color: #4f46e5;">Help Center</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:support@scanbite.com" style="color: #4f46e5;">support@scanbite.com</a></p>
      
      <p>Happy selling! 🚀</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2026 ScanBite. All rights reserved.<br>
      <a href="https://scanbite.com" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none;">Visit our website</a> | 
      <a href="https://scanbite.com/support" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none;">Support</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
